{"id":"336222842_Relations_in_the_maximal_pro-_quotients_of_absolute_Galois_groups","abstract":"We observe that some fundamental constructions in Galois theory can be used to obtain interesting restrictions on the structure of Galois groups of maximal p p -extensions of fields containing a primitive p p -th root of unity. This is an extension of some significant ideas of Demushkin, Labute, and Serre from local fields to all fields containing a primitive p p -th root of unity. Our techniques use certain natural simple Galois extensions together with some considerations in Galois cohomology and Massey products.","authors":["Jan Minac","Michael Rogelstad","Duy Tân Nguyêñ"],"meta":["October 2019Transactions of the American Mathematical Society 373(4):1","DOI:10.1090/tran/8003","Project: Profinite duality"],"references":["318671195_The_Kummerian_Property_and_Maximal_Pro-p_Galois_Groups","269997990_Triple_Massey_products_and_absolute_Galois_groups","269997749_Triple_Massey_products_vanish_over_all_fields","258113935_Detecting_Fast_solvability_of_equations_via_small_powerful_Galois_groups","251876269_Triple_Massey_products_and_Galois_theory","50305824_Galois_groups_and_cohomological_functors","45850541_Quotients_of_absolute_Galois_groups_which_determine_the_entire_Galoiscohomology","2126838_Automatic_realizations_of_Galois_groups_with_cyclic_quotient_of_order_pn","1774437_On_the_descending_central_sequence_of_absolute_Galois_groups","1733430_On_motivic_cohomology_with_Zl_coefficients","344482898_Analytic_Pro-P_Groups","321609934_Algebraic_Number_Theory","316807238_Graduate_Texts_in_Mathematics","316239725_Galois_Theory_of_p-Extensions","307716462_The_group_of_the_maximal_-extension_of_a_local_field","307714023_On_2-extensions_of_a_local_field","289080291_Structure_de_certains_pro-p-groupes_d'apres_Demuskin","281262543_Description_of_Galois_unipotent_extensions","272858062_Algebra","270593922_Construction_of_unipotent_Galois_extensions_and_Massey_products","267172136_On_the